metadata.description: Flipp Sounds presents for FYIM Art. Flipp Sounds - Genesis is a collection of 255 personalized musical works. Upon purchase, a handcrafted piece of music will be crafted based on the username who minted the project. For the genesis collection, the creator will include any lyrics, genre, or instruments to represent the minter of these items. The project director, Nick Flipp, is a professional music composer with over 200 original compositions. He is professional musician, a self proclaimed comedian, and content creator. Check out www.flippsounds.com for more info.
metadata.name: Flipp Sound - FYIM Art
